Response: { "sensor_id": "PM-25", "readings": [], "avg": 35.6, "min": 22.1, "max": 58.4 }

Question: Export the complete methane concentration history from sensor CH4-12 in the landfill site for the last 24 hours to ensure regulatory compliance.
Call: { "func_call": "export_sensor_data", "sensor_id": "CH4-12", "from": "2023-10-25T14:00:00Z", "to": "2023-10-26T14:00:00Z", "interval": "1h" }
